    cito:cites <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084058>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084064> ;
    dc:creator "Reyes, Jhoe; Brusa, Francisco" ;
    dc:title "Macrostomum quiritium Beklemischev 1951" ;
    trt:augmentsTaxonConcept <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Plantae/Macrostomum_quiritium_Beklemischev_1951> ;
    trt:publishedIn <http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4362.2.4> ;
    a trt:Treatment .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4362.2.4>
    dc:creator "Reyes, Jhoe; Brusa, Francisco" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "Species of Macrostomum (Macrostomorpha: Macrostomidae) from the coastal region of Lima, Peru, with comments on M. rostratum Papi, 1951" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084058>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084064> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084058>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Sample sites where species of Macrostomum were found. A, M. quiritium and M.tuba in Chillón River (sites 4, 5 and 6). B, M. rostratum in Humedales de Ventanilla (sites 1, 2 and 3)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1084058/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084064>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Photographs of a live specimen of Macrostomum quiritium Beklemischev, 1951. A, Dorsal view of a mature specimen; B–C, Posterior body region with details of the copulatory organs observed in dark and normal field; D–E, Photograph and schematic reconstruction of the penis stylet." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1084064/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

